<br>
Recently something came my way as an idea and it seems the backing and capital may be there to start this ....<br>
<br>
The idea was something similar to GamePro magazine and whatnot... but on a bi weekly basis... A magizine dedicated to the Online MMORPG Industry... which sales have balooned over the past 10 years to well over 8 billion a year in sales and revenue....<br>
<br>
But yet there is no bi weekly / monthly or whatnot publication that addresses this market.. <br>
<br>
In the publication would be break downs... and interviews...dealing with CSR and Creators of these games ranging from EQ to TheSIMS....zone breakdowns...even a back section called `Ploits..dealing with nuances of the game uber's keep to themselves..like certian pp camps and exp camps and whatnot..item camps and the like.... <br>
<br>
That being said the magazine would give out information that the players need to know...based on game information and creators, class information zone information and ..&quot;special&quot; knowledge.... <br>
<br>
Publishing, printing, design on this would be on the middle to middle low end in cost... as I am a Graphic Designer and have considerable writing talents and journalistic talents.... it would save on cost.... games covered would be along the lines of<br>
<br>
EQ<br>
EQ2<br>
SW:G<br>
BeyondEarth<br>
DAoC<br>
TSims<br>
NWN<br>
UO<br>
Diablo<br>
FPS like Quake and UT <br>
etc etc<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
I would like some feedback on this...  <br>
